Cellcom,SmsGate,provides,a,direct,SMS,Service,that,enables,organizations,and,business,entities,to,send,messages,in,bulk,to,the,cell,phones,of,their,employees,and,customers,This,service,is,available,through,a,browser,interface,or,it,can,be,accessed,programmatically,as,a,SOAP,API,The,Cellcom,SmsGate,website,and,the,API,documentation,are,provided,solely,in,Hebrew